 <H1>Process Isolation</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Processes and reconfigured hardware must be  isolated to enable robust, extensible systems
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Goal: Develop an Architectural Framework for Safe Adaptation
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Formalize OS notion of process and access control
<LI>Identify control points in base and adaptive hardware for access control 
<LI>Synthesize reverse maps for the OS protection constraints
<UL>
<LI>Isolation hardware
<LI>Fault mapping to OS semantics (meaningful faults to software) 
</UL><LI>Example: privilege level control, control register access, address generation, special instructions</UL></UL></P>
